{"type": "article", "id": 12803, "title": "木制水泥系列花盆", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-30T07:50:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122500AsRQKi3urkhwa5cv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自爱荷华的设计工作室 Vako Design 最近推出了一个木制和水泥系列花盆，最大限度地为植物营造自然的生长氛围。花盆的底部支架由木材制成，组装简单，不含任何五金材料。而当支架组装好之后，水泥花盆可以放置在上面，如果希望降低花盆高度，则只需要把支架倒立放置即可。花盆有不同的规格可以选择，搭配不同的花草使用。这是<a href=\"http://www.vakodesign.com/#/tessellamp-1/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140504zZBl4rd12JR0xeoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405051aZkSgpMxHJPbBcy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140505anUq6dcfVk0shDOl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140506YJFePGN8SKijdV5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405065zQsrpo6ikJZ9LBV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140508ydQszGg1LIVeimHB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140508fpKRSqZL0mvyrkJd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140508jdPxgObh1WckvU0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}